OL,8,     Ginfluenced, to the family
OL,9,     Gtensions that resulted from her
OL,10,     Ghuge ambition and success.
OL,11,G0255FWomen Who Rock
OL,12,     GTruth: With a helping hand from
OL,13,     Gthe likes of Mavis Staples, Janis
OL,14,     GJoplin and Chaka Khan, take a
OL,15,     Gtrip to the 1950s and 60s and the
OL,16,     Groots of rock and roll.
